metadata.name: Misty Shroud
metadata.description: " Misty Shroud" captures the haunting beauty of a country enshrouded in fog. The word "shroud" evokes a sense of mystery and intrigue, as if the fog is a veil that conceals the secrets of Japan's landscape and culture. The mist creates an otherworldly atmosphere, blurring the boundaries between reality and imagination, as if the land itself is a dream.
